remixlab.proscene

Class ClickBinding

  • java.lang.Object
    • remixlab.proscene.ClickBinding

  • public class ClickBinding
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents mouse click shortcuts.

    Mouse click shortcuts are defined with a specific number of clicks and can be of one out of two forms: 1. A mouse button; and, 2. A mouse button plus a key-modifier (such as the CTRL key).
